---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Content from "../../layouts/Content.astro";
const pageScript = "/js/pages/porters/json-to-java.js";
---
<Layout title="JSON to Java | TechRegistry"><Content title="JSON to Java" titleTag="Converter" starCount="5.2k stars" usageCount="7.8k uses today" version="v2.7.1" statusText="All Systems Operational" freeLabel="100% Free" privacyLabel="Client-Side Only" breadcrumbs={[{ label: "Home", href: "/" }, { label: "JSON to Java" }]}><div class="tool-page-shell" id="tool-page-root"><div class="card"><div class="card-body"><div class="tool-toolbar"><button id="tool-load-sample" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm" type="button">Load Sample</button><button id="tool-clear" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm" type="button">Clear</button><button id="tool-run" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" type="button">Generate Java</button></div><div class="tool-field-grid mt-3 mb-3"><div><label class="form-label" for="java-root">Root Class</label><input id="java-root" class="form-control" data-tool-field="rootClassName" /></div><div><label class="form-label" for="java-package">Package Name</label><input id="java-package" class="form-control" data-tool-field="packageName" /></div><div class="form-check"><input class="form-check-input" id="java-jackson" type="checkbox" data-tool-field="useJackson" checked /><label class="form-check-label" for="java-jackson">Add Jackson annotations</label></div></div><div id="tool-status" class="tool-status">Ready.</div><div class="tool-editors mt-3"><div><div class="tool-label-row"><label for="tool-input" class="form-label mb-0">JSON Input</label><span class="text-body-secondary">Paste a JSON object</span></div><textarea id="tool-input" class="form-control tool-code-input js-clipboard-source"></textarea></div><div><div class="tool-label-row"><label class="form-label mb-0">Generated Java</label><span class="text-body-secondary">Class output appears here</span></div><pre id="tool-output" class="tool-code-output"></pre></div></div></div></div><div class="card tool-details-card"><div class="card-header"><h3 class="card-title">About This JSON to Java Tool</h3></div><div class="card-body"><p>This JSON to Java converter helps create quick POJO-style models for DTOs, payload handling, and integration work.</p><p>It is useful for backend services, Android projects, and internal libraries where sample JSON needs a class starting point fast.</p><ul class="tool-detail-list"><li>Builds Java class skeletons from JSON objects.</li><li>Supports root class naming and package names.</li><li>Can add Jackson property annotations.</li></ul><div class="tool-points"><span class="tool-point"><i class="fa-solid fa-code"></i>Powered by browser-side JS</span></div></div></div></div></Content></Layout><script type="module" src={pageScript}></script>
